      Isn=E2=80=99t it ironic?
   =20
 =20

It is the official position of this column that you should never participat=
e in a corporate parody rap video, but can you, on your own time, record an=
 Alanis Morissette parody video about the collapse of your employer? I mean=
, I=E2=80=99m not gonna stop you. It helps that this  SVB-themed Alanis Mor=
issette parody is reasonably funny? And actually a pretty good summary of t=
he situation?=C2=A0=E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s a federal bailout, two minutes too=
 late.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=9CIt's like when you thought that T-bonds were safe,=
 but then Jerome Powell went and raised interest rates. It=E2=80=99s the sh=
are sale that just didn=E2=80=99t take, so now Elon Musk please buy us.=E2=
=80=9D

 =20
   =20
      Things happen
   =20
 =20

Signature Bank CEO in 2018: =E2=80=9CIn five years a number of banks   will=
 not be around because of blockchain technology.=E2=80=9D Patrick McKenzie:=
 =E2=80=9CThe world sits atop four elephants who stand astride the risk-fre=
e rate, and then it is interest rates all the way down.=E2=80=9D Nathan Tan=
kus: =E2=80=9CAll this nonsense can be eliminated by simply removing the ca=
p on deposit insurance, and admitting that  a bank deposit is money, and sh=
ould just be treated straightforwardly as such.=E2=80=9D Matt Klein: =E2=80=
=9CBanks are speculative investment funds grafted on top of  critical infra=
structure.=E2=80=9D Fed Weighs  Tougher Rules for Midsized Banks After SVB=
=E2=80=99s Collapse.=C2=A0Focus on SVB=E2=80=99s $180mn  D&O tower as US ac=
ts to avert wider banking crisis. Ukraine Wins UK Top Court Case Over $3 Bi=
llion   Bond Default.=C2=A0
