ote alongside the common, (2) there are now=C2=A0<em>more</em>=C2=A0APEs=C2=
=A0than common shares and=C2=A0(3) the APE holders have an incentive to vot=
e to allow the conversion, since the common trades at a much higher price t=
han the APEs.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Also though,=C2=A0(4=
) the APEs are <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/308=
