yLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; t=
ext-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-co=
lor: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> shareho=
lders sued</a>, saying that this whole structure is ridiculous and disenfra=
nchises shareholders.</li>
</ul>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When we <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/30845777.258426/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGlu=
aW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDItMjgvYW1jLXMtYXBlcy1oYXZlLXRvLXdhaXQ_Y21waWQ9QkJ=
