io. =E2=80=A6 The challenge for FDIC in a nutshell: these apparently dispar=
ate lending businesses are all deeply intertwined. High value to a franchis=
e buyer, questionable value to a piecemeal buyer. And if a buyer can't to t=
he earliest stage =E2=80=98investor dependent=E2=80=99 loans, can it hold o=
